<plan xmlns="http://www.eclipse.org/project/plan" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<release projectid="rt" version="1.0" />
	<introduction>
		<html:p>The EclipseLink 1.0 release is the first release after following the successful incubation of the contributed source from the Oracle TopLink product. This release focused on the migration of
			the code base to Eclipse along with JPA and MOXy enhancements as well as support for usage of EclipseLink in an OSGi environment. 
    </html:p>
	</introduction>

	<release_deliverables>
		<html:p>
			The 1.0 release and patch-sets are available for download
			<html:a href="http://www.eclipse.org/eclipselink/downloads/previous_releases.php#1.0">here</html:a>
			.
		</html:p>
		<html:p>
			The release offers:
			<html:ul>
				<html:li>ZIP file intended for standard JavaSE and JavaEE usage</html:li>
				<html:li>ZIP file provided of OSGi bundles</html:li>
				<html:li>Maven Repository</html:li>
			</html:ul>
		</html:p>
	</release_deliverables>

